===Etymology===
From {{etyl|fro|en}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|tuitiō||guard, protection, defense|lang=la}}, from {{term|tueri|tuēri|to watch, guard, see, observe}}. Compare {{term|intuition}}, {{term|tutor}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{enPR|to͞oĭ'shən}}, {{IPA|/tuˈɪʃən/}}, {{X-SAMPA|/tu"IS@n/}}
* {{rhymes|ɪʃən}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

